<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ن ص ت:</span> <span class="c2">(الْإِنْصَاتُ)</span> السُّكُوتُ وَالِاسْتِمَاعُ تَقُولُ: <span class="c2">(أَنْصَتَهُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(أَنْصَتَ)</span> لَهُ.<span class="c5"> قَالَ الشَّاعِرُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>إِذَا قَالَتْ حَذَامُ فَأَنْصِتُوهَا ... فَإِنَّ الْقَوْلَ مَا قَالَتْ حَذَامِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَيُرْوَى:</span> فَصَدِّقُوهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>